subject: Order Amending Schedule I.1 of the Financial Administration Act (Office of the Commissioner of Official Languages)
precis: Order amending SCHEDULE I.1 OF THE FINANCIAL ADMINISTRATION ACT (OFFICE OF THE COMMISSIONER OF OFFICIAL LANGUAGES) by replacing the reference to the Minister of Public Safety and Emergency Preparedness by reference to the Leader of the Government in the House of Commons.
